m\": 237, \"to\": 257}, {\"ngram\": \"the 400-metre freestyle\", \"from\": 275, \"to\": 298}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening night\", \"from\": 302, \"to\": 319}, {\"ngram\": \"finals\", \"from\": 323, \"to\": 329}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Although Australia's Olympic team will be confirmed on Saturday night, the performance assures Titmus a place with further opportunities to come over 200m, 800m and relays.\", \"from\": 367, \"to\": 539, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 376, \"end\": 385, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9999926357557475, \"rank\": 7.349847533906561e-06, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 462, \"end\": 468, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Titmus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Saturday night\", \"from\": 422, \"to\": 436}, {\"ngram\": \"the performance\", \"from\": 438, \"to\": 453}, {\"ngram\": \"a place\", \"from\": 469, \"to\": 476}, {\"ngram\": \"further opportunities\", \"from\": 482, \"to\": 503}, {\"ngram\": \"800m\", \"from\": 523, \"to\": 527}, {\"ngram\": \"relays\", \"from\": 532, \"to\": 538}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's a nice feeling to finally say 'I am going'.\", \"from\": 541, \"to\": 590, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a nice feeling\", \"from\": 547, \"to\": 561}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's nice to actually have the box ticked,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 591, \"to\": 644, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the box\", \"from\": 618, \"to\": 625}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's a funny feeling having your PB (personal best) as the world record.\", \"from\": 646, \"to\": 719, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 680, \"en