", \"from\": 1156, \"to\": 1245, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1233, \"end\": 1239, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Titmus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this morning\", \"from\": 1163, \"to\": 1175}, {\"ngram\": \"a chance\", \"from\": 1197, \"to\": 1205}, {\"ngram\": \"the record\", \"from\": 1219, \"to\": 1229}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The goal is not to swim my best here, the goal is to book a ticket [to the Olympics], so I am excited to see what I can do in Paris.\", \"from\": 1247, \"to\": 1380, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1374, \"end\": 1379, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999999434749, \"rank\": 5.650325417553565e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The goal\", \"from\": 1248, \"to\": 1256}, {\"ngram\": \"the goal\", \"from\": 1286, \"to\": 1294}, {\"ngram\": \"a ticket\", \"from\": 1306, \"to\": 1314}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1319, \"to\": 1331}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think I have timed my prep perfectly.\\\"\", \"from\": 1381, \"to\": 1421, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my prep\", \"from\": 1402, \"to\": 1409}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The former Riverside and Launceston Aquatic swimmer, who now represents St Peters Western, clocked 3:55.44 to lead home Lani Pallister (4:02.27) and training partner Jamie Perkins (4:04.38).\", \"from\": 1423, \"to\": 1614, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1434, \"end\": 1443, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Riverside_International_Raceway\", \"score\": 0.9996869789483898, \"rank\": 0.000313119057415519, \"text\": \"Riverside\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org