"to\": 1611}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Trials is a bit of a free shot for me,\\\" Titmus added.\", \"from\": 1616, \"to\": 1670, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1657, \"end\": 1663, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Titmus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Trials\", \"from\": 1617, \"to\": 1623}, {\"ngram\": \"a bit\", \"from\": 1627, \"to\": 1632}, {\"ngram\": \"a free shot\", \"from\": 1636, \"to\": 1647}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not have to worry about getting under a qualifying time, so if I stuff up, I have the luxury that I'd probably still be on the team.\", \"from\": 1672, \"to\": 1810, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a qualifying time\", \"from\": 1716, \"to\": 1733}, {\"ngram\": \"the luxury\", \"from\": 1760, \"to\": 1770}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 1801, \"to\": 1809}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So it's about trying new things and to win, you always have to try new things.\", \"from\": 1812, \"to\": 1891, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"new things\", \"from\": 1834, \"to\": 1844}, {\"ngram\": \"new things\", \"from\": 1880, \"to\": 1890}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You can not just expect to do the same thing and keep winning.\", \"from\": 1892, \"to\": 1954, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the same thing\", \"from\": 1922, \"to\": 1936}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have not seen my splits but if I am that far under, I think that gives me confidence that I took it out and I was quite fearless.\\\"\", \"from\": 1956, \"to\": 2089, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my splits\", \"from\": 1973, \"to\": 1982}, {\"ngram\": \"confidence\", \"from\": 2033, \"to\": 2043}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Titmus, whose family moved from Launceston to Brisbane in 2015, had earli